# Wallet ethcc Rules

## Wallet ethcc Summary

`@/example/wallet-ethcc` is part of Frak monorepo and is designed to provide a user interface for interacting with the Frak Wallet, specifically tailored for the EthCC event. This package integrates various components and functionalities to enhance user engagement with blockchain interactions, leveraging modern web technologies.
Project is written in TypeScript using React 19, React Router v7, Radix UI and Shadcn UI for components, React Query for server state management, Viem and Wagmi for blockchain.

